{"tid":1726371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特急!200萬人已有一半人慢慢變藍絲","createTime":"2019-11-16T06:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T07:39:00.000Z","uid":176996,"like":20,"dislike":107,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e74ed937a7dd2b8e8fb1cc8a50cbfb2c1f0b86","tid":1726371,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:32:39.000Z","msg":"Sorry標題黨，我想大家唸下如果上次200萬人行出來抗惡法，現在還有多少人呢?<br />\n<br />\n本人親身例子，有兩個曾經出來遊行的和理非同事，一個自問貪生怕死說怕被捉，自九月至今已經唔敢再行出來(包括人鏈和你shop)，另一個由之前同情學生，現在開始說黑衫暴力。我發現，他們有共通點:<br />\n1)自從宣佈條例撤回後，已收貨<br />\n2)一直主張合法和平示威<br />\n3)一直主張反暴力<br />\n<br />\n以上的人，可以稱為「黃皮藍心」收貨撚，以下連結可以飛去10:20開始聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AV-PiLGzvD8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAV-PiLGzvD8&d=x8osXdNjm17U7TcHCf5EXpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=15a94564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AV-PiLGzvD8</a><br />\n<br />\n利申:4年前曾經是淺藍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SjzC7x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSjzC7x0.png&h=82ab5372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdQuYEG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdQuYEG.jpg&h=b1bf660e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FjNUqjH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjNUqjH.png&h=5ff195b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b445d1006e237801681257846e6ac1632bc5d10b","tid":1726371,"uid":176996,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:32:58.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"6dec2e7072bc5b9ed1aca5474110abf237a9bdcf","tid":1726371,"uid":43041,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:33:13.000Z","msg":"標題黨死全家斷子絕孫不得好死"},{"pid":"b012a7992648b5cd80a91235ab598e8b4eb51cc3","tid":1726371,"uid":37375,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:33:13.000Z","msg":"fuck off 標題黨"},{"pid":"0a4dfee8df08e82d802377c1342880f4710275f8